{"tid":2160713,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[確定立場]重返議會之泛民議員一律當藍絲處理","createTime":"2020-08-17T06:43:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T09:14:44.000Z","uid":155126,"like":17,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3cdb91f0b37e79a135a782c865dcd5650bac6128","tid":2160713,"uid":155126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T06:43:52.000Z","msg":"對家劇本以抗疫為由 打壓民主選舉 <br />\n佢哋心知泛民已無力阻擋任何法案通過<br />\n<br />\n相反<br />\n<br />\n令議員全體重返議會可以造成一個<span class=\"red\">假象</span><br />\n<span class=\"red\">政府尊重不同聲音 社會依然 享有民主</span><br />\n如果民主派拒總辭 只會配合敵人目的<br />\n<br />\n過去一年 我哋深知議會已經名存實亡 無法反映民意<br />\n今次總辭係要實實在在向市民、國際反映立法會以及港共政府既不義 重返議會只會成為敵方之回血劍"},{"pid":"2c778809aea708044b98c2be376aed838dde0ac0","tid":2160713,"uid":155126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T06:44:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35217c79cd2e8ed82c30ddb1fa1eba3fd7d0deaf","tid":2160713,"uid":155126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T06:47:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90062c40d8e7c51784a266a4039f17849c8d67d9","tid":2160713,"uid":57542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T07:56:54.000Z","msg":"泛民就係仆街"},{"pid":"31a1a5863d8979fd99f1e465c37ca24327c7648f","tid":2160713,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T07:57:55.000Z","msg":"條底線係由市民決定佢地應唔應該返議會"},{"pid":"940e3bc43c68e77316809b93370d2ef60991d734","tid":2160713,"uid":155126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:14:44.000Z","msg":"推"}]}